The paper deals with optimization and learning in a cognitive radio system, which involves sensing and accessing available spectrum channels opportunistically. This falls under the domain of information theory (cs.IT) and networked systems (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the use of cost-aware strategies, which is a topic of interest in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper deals with decision-making and control in a dynamic system, which is a topic of interest in control systems (cs.SY).
